sys_update_xml.payload:
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update table="content_css"><content_css action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><name>bootstrap.carousel.css</name><style>/* GLOBAL STYLES
-------------------------------------------------- */
/* Padding below the footer and lighter body text */

body {
  padding-bottom: 40px;
  color: #5a5a5a;
}



/* CUSTOMIZE THE NAVBAR
-------------------------------------------------- */

/* Special class on .container surrounding .navbar, used for positioning it into place. */
.navbar-wrapper {
  position: absolute;
  top: 0;
  right: 0;
  left: 0;
  z-index: 20;
}

/* Flip around the padding for proper display in narrow viewports */
.navbar-wrapper .container {
  padding-right: 0;
  padding-left: 0;
}
.navbar-wrapper .navbar {
  padding-right: 15px;
  padding-left: 15px;
}


/* CUSTOMIZE THE CAROUSEL
-------------------------------------------------- */

/* Carousel base class */
.carousel {
  height: 500px;
  margin-bottom: 60px;
}
/* Since positioning the image, we need to help out the caption */
.carousel-caption {
  z-index: 10;
}

/* Declare heights because of positioning of img element */
.carousel .item {
  height: 500px;
  background-color: #777;
}
.carousel-inner > .item > img {
  position: absolute;
  top: 0;
  left: 0;
  min-width: 100%;
  height: 500px;
}



/* MARKETING CONTENT
-------------------------------------------------- */

/* Pad the edges of the mobile views a bit */
.marketing {
  padding-right: 15px;
  padding-left: 15px;
}

/* Center align the text within the three columns below the carousel */
.marketing .col-lg-4 {
  margin-bottom: 20px;
  text-align: center;
}
.marketing h2 {
  font-weight: normal;
}
.marketing .col-lg-4 p {
  margin-right: 10px;
  margin-left: 10px;
}


/* Featurettes
------------------------- */

.featurette-divider {
  margin: 80px 0; /* Space out the Bootstrap <hr> more */
}

/* Thin out the marketing headings */
.featurette-heading {
  font-weight: 300;
  line-height: 1;
  letter-spacing: -1px;
}



/* RESPONSIVE CSS
-------------------------------------------------- */

@media (min-width: 768px) {

  /* Remove the edge padding needed for mobile */
  .marketing {
    padding-right: 0;
    padding-left: 0;
  }

  /* Navbar positioning foo */
  .navbar-wrapper {
    margin-top: 20px;
  }
  .navbar-wrapper .container {
    /*
    padding-right: 15px;
    padding-left:  15px;
    */
  }
  .navbar-wrapper .navbar {
    padding-right: 0;
    padding-left:  0;
  }

  /* The navbar becomes detached from the top, so we round the corners */
  .navbar-wrapper .navbar {
    border-radius: 4px;
  }

  /* Bump up size of carousel content */
  .carousel-caption p {
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    font-size: 21px;
    line-height: 1.4;
  }

  .featurette-heading {
    font-size: 50px;
  }
}

@media (min-width: 992px) {
  .featurette-heading {
    margin-top: 120px;
  }
}
</style><sys_created_by>admin_SHARE</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2014-04-17 17:57:23</sys_created_on><sys_id>0a8df947eb00210093d6c63ca206fe06</sys_id><sys_mod_count>8</sys_mod_count><sys_updated_by>eric.szonyi_SHARE</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2014-06-03 15:29:59</sys_updated_on><type>local</type><url/></content_css></record_update>

<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update table="sys_script_include"><sys_script_include action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><active>true</active><client_callable>true</client_callable><description/><name>CmsCartUtils</name><script><![CDATA[var CmsCartUtils = Class.create();
CmsCartUtils.prototype = Object.extendsObject(AbstractAjaxProcessor, {
    getCartCount: function() {
        var cnt = 0;
        var c = new GlideRecord('sc_cart_item');
        c.addQuery('active','true');
        c.addQuery('cart.requested_for',gs.getUserID());
        c.query()
        while (c.next()) {
            cnt += parseInt(c.quantity);
        }
        var arr = cnt.toString().split('.');
        cnt = arr[0];
        return cnt;
    },

    type: 'CmsCartUtils'
});
]]></script><sys_created_by>admin_SHARE</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2014-07-28 04:12:01</sys_created_on><sys_id>f8c218730ccea100afe4c3eb0a60b480</sys_id><sys_mod_count>0</sys_mod_count><sys_updated_by>admin_SHARE</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2014-07-28 04:12:01</sys_updated_on></sys_script_include><sys_app_file action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><customer_update>true</customer_update><publish_override/><replace_on_upgrade>false</replace_on_upgrade><restore/><sys_app/><sys_code>!!6@H/</sys_code><sys_created_by>admin_SHARE</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2014-07-28 04:12:01</sys_created_on><sys_id>79d294730ccea100afe4c3eb0a60b4f6</sys_id><sys_mod_count>1</sys_mod_count><sys_name>CmsCartUtils</sys_name><sys_parent/><sys_path>!!6@H/</sys_path><sys_policy/><sys_source_deleted>false</sys_source_deleted><sys_source_id>f8c218730ccea100afe4c3eb0a60b480</sys_source_id><sys_source_table>sys_script_include</sys_source_table><sys_type>code</sys_type><sys_update_name>sys_script_include_f8c218730ccea100afe4c3eb0a60b480</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>admin_SHARE</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2014-07-28 04:12:01</sys_updated_on></sys_app_file></record_update>

<j:jelly trim="false" xmlns:j="jelly:core" xmlns:g="glide" xmlns:j2="null" xmlns:g2="null">

<!--

   When a search is issued, results from this search operation will be driven the the search page
   that is configured in your Content Management configuration page. You can access the configuration page
   under Content Management -> Configuration.

   Once there, change the "Search Form" field to point to whichever page you want the search to point to.

  -->



 <form class="navbar-form navbar-right" name="content_search" id="content_search" action="content_search.do" method="post" style="padding-left:5px; padding-bottom:10px;">
                       <input type="HIDDEN" value="${current_page.getSiteID()}" name="sysparm_current_site"/>            
                       <span class="globalSearch contextSearch" >
                           <g:call function="sport_text_search_input" size="24"/> 
                       </span> 
                 
 </form>
 <script eval="true">
  var ajax = new GlideAjax("TextSearchAjax");
  ajax.addParam("sysparm_name", "recent");
  ajax.getXML(adjustSearchResponse);

  function adjustSearchResponse(request) {
    var answer =  request.responseXML.documentElement.getAttribute("answer");

    if (answer != null) {
    	var gcm = new GwtContextMenu('context_search');
	    gcm.clear();
        if (answer.indexOf("xyzzyx") != 0) {
	    	var db = answer.split("^");
	    	for (var i = 0; i != db.length; i++) {
			     gcm.addHref(db[i], "content_search('"+db[i]+"')");
		    }
		} else gcm.addLabel(answer.substr(6));
    }
  } 


function content_search(term) {
   gel('content_search').sysparm_search.value=term;
   gel('content_search').submit();
}
 </script>

</j:jelly></xml></sys_ui_macro></record_update>

<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update table="sys_ui_macro"><sys_ui_macro action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><active>true</active><category>list</category><description/><media_type/><name>sport_datatable_sc_req_item</name><sys_created_by>eric.szonyi_SHARE</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2014-05-21 17:07:03</sys_created_on><sys_id>6318bc8e4df8adc0bc95842eaf53549e</sys_id><sys_mod_count>4</sys_mod_count><sys_updated_by>eric.szonyi_SHARE</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2014-06-18 18:52:07</sys_updated_on><xml><?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<j:jelly trim="false" xmlns:j="jelly:core" xmlns:g="glide" xmlns:j2="null" xmlns:g2="null">
  <div class="table-responsive">
    <table class="table table-hover" id="requestTable">
      <thead>
        <tr>
          <th>Number</th>
          <th>Description</th>
          <th>Stage</th>
          <th>Updated</th>
          <th>Updated By</th>
        </tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody>
      <g:for_each_record file="${current}" max="${jvar_max_entries}">
         <tr> 
              <g:content_summarizer content="${current}"/>
         </tr> 
      </g:for_each_record>
      </tbody>
    </table>
  </div>
  <script>
$j(document).ready(function(){
    var ot = $j('#requestTable').dataTable({
        "order": [[ 3, "desc" ]]
    });
    $j('#reqTotal').text(ot.fnSettings().fnRecordsTotal());
});
  </script>
</j:jelly></xml></sys_ui_macro></record_update>

sys_update_xml.payload:
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update table="content_block_programmatic"><content_block_programmatic action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><active>true</active><category>general</category><condition/><conditional>false</conditional><frame/><logged_on>false</logged_on><name>Live Feed</name><programmatic_content><?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" ?>
<j:jelly trim="false" xmlns:j="jelly:core" xmlns:g="glide" xmlns:j2="null" xmlns:g2="null">

	<j:if test="${gs.isLoggedIn() != true}">
<div id="output_messages">
	<!-- info messages -->
	<div class="system_message outputmsg_info">
		<table cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0" class="background_transparent">
			<tr>
				<td class="message_image"><img src="images/outputmsg_info.gifx" alt="${gs.getMessage('Informational Message')}" width="16" height="16"/></td>
				<td width="100%">

				<b>Oh Snap, you are looking for "Live Company Feed" aren't you?</b>  You must be logged in to view and participate.

				</td>
			</tr>
		</table>
	</div>
</div>




</j:if>
	<j:if test="${gs.isLoggedIn() == true}">

		<!-- blocks don't have access to request parameters so get what we need from render properties -->
		<j:set var="sysparm_feed_type" value="${RP.getParameterValue('sysparm_feed_type')}"/>
		<j:set var="sysparm_group_id" value="${RP.getParameterValue('sysparm_group_id')}"/>
		<!-- page more appropriate for mobile browsers -->
		<g:requires name="styles/LiveFeedIncludes.css" includes="true" />
		<g:requires name="styles/live_feed_small.css" />
		<g:requires name="scripts/LiveFeedIncludes.js" includes="true" />
		<div style="margin-left: 3px; margin-right: 3px;">
			<g:inline template="live_feed_config_desktop.xml"/>
			<g:inline template="live_feed_config.xml"/>
			<!--<g:inline template="live_feed_center.xml"/>-->

			<table width="100%" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0">
				<tbody>
					<tr>
						<td width="80%">
							<div id="center_column" class="live_feed_column live_feed_column_center" style="width:100% !important; float: none;">
								<g:inline template="live_feed_center.xml"/>
							</div>
						</td>
						<td valign="top"  width="20%">
							<div id="left_column" class="live_feed_column" style="width:20% !important;">
								<g:inline template="live_feed_left.xml"/>
							</div>
						</td>
					</tr>
				</tbody>
			</table>
		</div>
	</j:if>
</j:jelly></programmatic_content><sys_class_name>content_block_programmatic</sys_class_name><sys_created_by>mark.odonnell_SHARE</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2011-06-20 22:43:44</sys_created_on><sys_id>7c561487ef130000914304167b225646</sys_id><sys_mod_count>1</sys_mod_count><sys_updated_by>mark.odonnell@snc_SHARE</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2013-09-29 22:22:35</sys_updated_on><two_phase>true</two_phase></content_block_programmatic></record_update>

<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update table="content_css"><content_css action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><name>sport_iframe.dynamic.css</name><style>HTML[data-doctype=true] BUTTON, HTML[data-doctype=true] INPUT.button {
    border-color: #${cms.sport.color.button};
    color: #${cms.sport.color.button};
}
HTML[data-doctype=true] BUTTON:hover, HTML[data-doctype=true] INPUT.button:hover {
    background-color: #${cms.sport.color.button};
    color: #ffffff;
}
HTML[data-doctype=true] DIV.vcr_controls {
    border-top: solid 1px #${cms.sport.color.button};
    border-bottom: solid 1px #${cms.sport.color.button};
}
HTML[data-doctype=true] .tabs2_active {
    border-top: 5px solid #${cms.sport.color.accent};
}
HTML[data-doctype="true"] INPUT:focus, HTML[data-doctype="true"] TEXTAREA:focus, HTML[data-doctype="true"] BUTTON:focus, HTML[data-doctype="true"] INPUT.button:focus, HTML[data-doctype="true"] A.menu:focus, HTML[data-doctype="true"] A IMG:focus, HTML[data-doctype="true"] SELECT:focus {
    border: 1px solid #${cms.sport.color.accent};
    box-shadow: 0px 0px 5px #${cms.sport.color.accent};
}
HTML[data-doctype=true] BUTTON[name*=vcr_]:hover {
    background-color: #${cms.sport.color.accent};
}
HTML[data-doctype=true] BUTTON[name*=vcr_] {
    border: 1px solid #${cms.sport.color.accent};
    color: #${cms.sport.color.accent};
}
HTML[data-doctype=true] A.navigation_link {
    color: #${cms.sport.color.accent};
}
a.service_catalog > strong {
    color: #${cms.sport.color.accent};
}

   <g:evaluate var="jvar_time_text">
     var d1 = current.sys_updated_on.getGlideObject().getRaw();
     var d2 = Packages.com.glide.glideobject.GlideDateTime().getRaw();
     
     var diff = gs.dateDiff(current.sys_updated_on.getDisplayValue(), gs.nowDateTime(), true);
     var msg;
     if (3600 * 12 > diff) {
       var s = Packages.com.glide.ui.jelly.tags.mergedata.HistoryTag2().translatedTimeDifferenceString(d2, d1);
       if (s == null)
         msg = "${gs.getMessage('Just now')}";
       else
         msg = s.toLowerCase() + '${gs.getMessage(" ago")}';
     } else {
       var session = gs.getSession();
       var tf = session.getTimeFormat();
       session.setTimeFormat(" ");
       msg = trim(current.sys_updated_on.getDisplayValue());
       session.setTimeFormat(tf);
     }
     msg;
   </g:evaluate>

});

<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update table="sys_ui_script"><sys_ui_script action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><active>true</active><description/><global>false</global><name>sport.utils</name><script><![CDATA[$j(document).ready(function () {
    //configure tooltips for category browsing
    //$j('.tip').tooltip();

    /* apply bootstrap styles to dropdowns */
    $j('select').addClass('form-control');

    //reload the page after the settings modal closes
    $j('#propsModal').on('hidden.bs.modal',function(e) {
        location.reload();
    });

});



/* wait until the GSFT_MAIN iframe is fully loaded */
$j("#gsft_main").load(function() {
    /* load the iframe css */
    var cssLink = document.createElement("link")
    cssLink.href = "345b1b73790de540f110a6fa63ddf1ee.cssdbx";
    cssLink.rel = "stylesheet";
    cssLink.type = "text/css";
    frames['gsft_main'].document.body.appendChild(cssLink);

    /* load the dynamic iframe css */
    var cssLink = document.createElement("link")
    cssLink.href = "sportdynamiccss.do?name=sport_iframe.dynamic.css?sysparm_stack=no";
    cssLink.rel = "stylesheet";
    cssLink.type = "text/css";
    frames['gsft_main'].document.body.appendChild(cssLink);

	/* load IE9 fix CSS for IFrames with Bootstrap */
    if (navigator.userAgent.indexOf('MSIE 9') != -1) {
        var cssLink = document.createElement("link")
        cssLink.href = "ca6de3f57cbae100afe4aa6048207ca1.cssdbx";
        cssLink.rel = "stylesheet";
        cssLink.type = "text/css";
        document.getElementsByTagName("head")[0].appendChild(cssLink);
    }

    /* get the iframe itself */
    var gsft = $j("#gsft_main").contents();

    /* apply bootstrap styles to dropdowns */
    gsft.find('select').addClass('form-control');

    /* apply bootstrap styles to lists */
    gsft.find('table.wideDataList.list_table').addClass('table');

    /* apply bootstrap styles to info messages */
    gsft.find('div.outputmsg_info').addClass('alert').addClass('alert-info').removeClass('outputmsg_info');
    gsft.find('div.outputmsg_error').addClass('alert').addClass('alert-danger').removeClass('outputmsg_error');

	/* fix continue shopping button */
    gsft.find('a#catalog_cart_continue_shopping').attr('href','request.do');

	/* fix back to catalog button */
    gsft.find('button.catalog.catalog_previous:contains("Back to Catalog")').replaceWith("<form action='request.do'><input class='button catalog catalog_previous' type='submit' value='Back to Catalog' /></form>");


    /* script to make ajax call to update cart */
    function updateSportCart() {
        var ga = new GlideAjax('CmsCartUtils');
        ga.addParam('sysparm_name', 'getCartCount');
        ga.getXML(CartCountParse);
        function CartCountParse(response) {
            var answer = response.responseXML.documentElement.getAttribute('answer');
            var newCount = answer;
            $j('#mini-cart-count', top.document).text(newCount);
        }
    }

    /* update the cart whenever the iframe reloads */
    updateSportCart();

    /* string version of script for injection */
    var updateCartScript = "var ga = new GlideAjax('CmsCartUtils');";
    updateCartScript += "ga.addParam('sysparm_name', 'getCartCount');";
    updateCartScript += "ga.getXML(CartCountParse);";
    updateCartScript += "function CartCountParse(response) {";
    updateCartScript += "var answer = response.responseXML.documentElement.getAttribute('answer');";
    updateCartScript += "var newCount = answer;";
    updateCartScript += "$j('#mini-cart-count', top.document).text(newCount);";
    updateCartScript += "}";


    /* inject cart update script to the add to cart button */
    var addCartButton = gsft.find('a[onclick*="addToCart();"]');
    var addCartButtonScript = addCartButton.attr('onclick');
    var theFunc = addCartButtonScript.replace("return false;",updateCartScript + "return false;");
    addCartButton.attr('onclick', theFunc);

});

]]></script><sys_created_by>eric.szonyi_SHARE</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2014-05-04 02:17:58</sys_created_on><sys_id>1299c6d44de8ed80bc95842eaf535433</sys_id><sys_mod_count>274</sys_mod_count><sys_updated_by>admin_SHARE</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2014-10-22 03:31:37</sys_updated_on></sys_ui_script><sys_app_file action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><customer_update>true</customer_update><publish_override/><replace_on_upgrade>false</replace_on_upgrade><restore/><sys_app/><sys_code>!!6$./</sys_code><sys_created_by>eric.szonyi_SHARE</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2014-05-04 02:17:58</sys_created_on><sys_id>08104cd27da5a100afe443a59ebea882</sys_id><sys_mod_count>0</sys_mod_count><sys_name>sport.utils</sys_name><sys_parent/><sys_path>!!6$./</sys_path><sys_policy/><sys_source_deleted>false</sys_source_deleted><sys_source_id>1299c6d44de8ed80bc95842eaf535433</sys_source_id><sys_source_table>sys_ui_script</sys_source_table><sys_type>code</sys_type><sys_update_name>sys_ui_script_1299c6d44de8ed80bc95842eaf535433</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>admin_SHARE</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2014-10-22 03:31:37</sys_updated_on></sys_app_file></record_update>

<j:jelly trim="false" xmlns:j="jelly:core" xmlns:g="glide" xmlns:j2="null" xmlns:g2="null">
   <j:set var="jvar_edit_link" value="javascript:replaceThisCell(e, 'content_block_menu.do?sysparm_query=type=blocks')" />

<p>  A horizontal blocks menu displays a series of blocks horizontally until the horizontal space is exhausted and then they will stack. They are most often seen in the main content area of pages.</p>

<g:evaluate var="jvar_clicklink_id" jelly="true">
  if ("${jvar_RP.media}" == "preview")
    "clickHereHorzBlocksMenuPreview";
  else
    "clickHereHorzBlocksMenu";
</g:evaluate>
<div id="${jvar_clicklink_id}" name="${jvar_clicklink_id}">
   <p>
      <a class="web" onclick="replaceThisCell(event, 'content_block_menu.do?sysparm_query=type=blocks')">Click here</a> to configure this reusable menu block.
   </p>
</div>
<script eval="true">
   if (window.glideGrid === undefined) { // hide link in preview mode
      var els = document.getElementsByName("clickHereHorzBlocksMenu");
      if (els)
         for (var i = els.length - 1;i >= 0;i--)
            els[i].style.display = "none";
   } else { // else hide link in add content dialog
      var e = gel("clickHereHorzBlocksMenuPreview");
      if (e)
         e.style.display = "none";
   }
</script>

<div style="padding:5px;">
   <p align="center"><img src="cms_menu_example_horz_blocks.pngx"/></p>
</div>

<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update table="content_css"><content_css action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><name>owl.carousel.css</name><style>/* 
 * 	Core Owl Carousel CSS File
 *	v1.3.3
 */

/* clearfix */
.owl-carousel .owl-wrapper:after {
	content: ".";
	display: block;
	clear: both;
	visibility: hidden;
	line-height: 0;
	height: 0;
}
/* display none until init */
.owl-carousel{
	display: none;
	position: relative;
	width: 100%;
	-ms-touch-action: pan-y;
}
.owl-carousel .owl-wrapper{
	display: none;
	position: relative;
	-webkit-transform: translate3d(0px, 0px, 0px);
}
.owl-carousel .owl-wrapper-outer{
	overflow: hidden;
	position: relative;
	width: 100%;
}
.owl-carousel .owl-wrapper-outer.autoHeight{
	-webkit-transition: height 500ms ease-in-out;
	-moz-transition: height 500ms ease-in-out;
	-ms-transition: height 500ms ease-in-out;
	-o-transition: height 500ms ease-in-out;
	transition: height 500ms ease-in-out;
}
	
.owl-carousel .owl-item{
	float: left;
}
.owl-controls .owl-page,
.owl-controls .owl-buttons div{
	cursor: pointer;
}
.owl-controls {
	-webkit-user-select: none;
	-khtml-user-select: none;
	-moz-user-select: none;
	-ms-user-select: none;
	user-select: none;
	-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);
}

/* mouse grab icon */
.grabbing { 
    cursor:url(grabbing.png) 8 8, move;
}

/* fix */
.owl-carousel  .owl-wrapper,
.owl-carousel  .owl-item{
	-webkit-backface-visibility: hidden;
	-moz-backface-visibility:    hidden;
	-ms-backface-visibility:     hidden;
  -webkit-transform: translate3d(0,0,0);
  -moz-transform: translate3d(0,0,0);
  -ms-transform: translate3d(0,0,0);
}

<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update table="content_type"><content_type action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><content_site display_value="UA2">a90ef6b6eb00210093d6c63ca206fe6b</content_site><detail><?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<j:jelly trim="false" xmlns:j="jelly:core" xmlns:g="glide" xmlns:j2="null" xmlns:g2="null">
  <g:evaluate>
     var gr = new GlideRecord('content_block_iframe');
     gr.initialize();
     gr.frame_name = 'gsft_main';
     gr.url = "kb_view.do?sys_kb_id=${current.sys_id}";
     gr.sizing = 'expand';
     gr.putCurrent();
  </g:evaluate>
  <g:render_content_block_iframe />
  <g:evaluate>
     gr.popCurrent();
  </g:evaluate>
</j:jelly></detail><detail_page display_value="UA2 - Knowledge Detail">a80553774d98ad80bc95842eaf53541b</detail_page><gauge_page/><media_type/><summary><?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<j:jelly trim="false" xmlns:j="jelly:core" xmlns:g="glide" xmlns:j2="null" xmlns:g2="null">
   <g:evaluate var="jvar_time_text">
     var msg;
     if (0 >= gs.dateDiff(current.published, current.sys_updated_on.getGlideObject().getDate(), true))
       msg = "${gs.getMessage('Published')} " + current.published;
     else {
       msg = "${gs.getMessage('Updated')} ";
       var d1 = current.sys_updated_on.getGlideObject().getRaw();
       var d2 = Packages.com.glide.glideobject.GlideDateTime().getRaw();
       var diff = gs.dateDiff(current.sys_updated_on.getDisplayValue(), gs.nowDateTime(), true);
       if (3600 * 12 > diff) {
         var s = Packages.com.glide.ui.jelly.tags.mergedata.HistoryTag2().translatedTimeDifferenceString(d2, d1);
         if (s == null)
           msg += "${gs.getMessage('just now')}";
         else
           msg += s.toLowerCase() + '${gs.getMessage(" ago")}';
       } else {
         var session = gs.getSession();
         var tf = session.getTimeFormat();
         session.setTimeFormat(" ");
         msg += trim(current.sys_updated_on.getDisplayValue());
         session.setTimeFormat(tf);
       }
     }
     msg;
   </g:evaluate>
   <g:content_link type="${jvar_type}" content_link_class="${jvar_content_link_class}">
     <g:highlighter search="${sysparm_search}">${current.short_description}</g:highlighter><div class="cms_knowledge_link_subtext">${jvar_time_text}</div>
   </g:content_link>
</j:jelly></summary><sys_created_by>eric.szonyi@snc.admin_SHARE</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2014-05-02 14:38:46</sys_created_on><sys_id>5fdf56774d18ad80bc95842eaf53547b</sys_id><sys_mod_count>5</sys_mod_count><sys_updated_by>eric.szonyi_SHARE</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2014-06-05 02:37:55</sys_updated_on><two_phase>false</two_phase><type>kb_knowledge</type></content_type></record_update>

sys_update_xml.payload:
truekbfalsefalseSport Documentation
  • Editing Header Navigation Items
    1. Goto Content Management > Dynamic > Sport Dynamic Header
    2. Add or modify links under the tag - <ul class="nav navbar-nav">
  • Configuring Lists on TODOs Page
    1. To change a filter or sort for a list, goto Content Management > Lists
    2. To change the name of a list, goto Content Management > Dynamic > Sport Dynamic Todos
    3. To add a new list to the page:
      1. Create a list - Content Management > Lists
      2. Create a content type - Content Management > Sites > Sport > Content Types (Related List)
      3. Create a UI Macro similar to sport_datatable_change - System UI > UI Macros
      4. Add a new section to the dynamic block > Content Management > Dynamic > Sport Dynamic Todos
  • Updating Images on Home Page Carousel
    1. Update the images called carousel0.jpg, carousel1.jpg, carousel2.jpg - Content Management > Images
  • Modifying Category Blocks
    1. Goto Content Management > Navigation Menus
      1. For the Home page, open Sport Home Block Menu and edit items
      2. For the Request page, open Sport Request Categories Block Menu and edit items
  • Adding A New Service Catalog Category
    1. Create a new IFrame (you can copy Order Hardware) and change the sys_id in the URL to the sys_id of the new Category record - Content Management > IFrames
    2. Create a new page and add the new IFrame to it - Content Management > Sites > Sport > New Page
    3. Goto the categories menu - Content Management > Sport Request Categories Block Menu
    4. Select the appropriate menu section from the related list
    5. Add a new Menu Item and point it to a Content Page
  • Changing Feedback Survey
    1. Goto System UI > UI Scripts and open sport.utils
    2. Near the top there is an fm_options section > change the iframe_url parameter to the new survey
  • 3rd Party Libraries or Code
    1. Bootstrap (getbootstrap.com) - Used for the foundation of the entire site
    2. Owl Carousel (http://www.owlgraphic.com/owlcarousel/) - Used for the carousel functionality on the Request page
    3. Pick-A-Color (http://lauren.github.io/pick-a-color/) - Used for the color picker on the Settings Page
    4. CSS Imageless Floating Button (http://alexpeattie.com/projects/feedback_button/) - Used for the feedback button



    Anatomy of the Site

sys_update_xml.payload:
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update table="content_css"><content_css action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><name>owl.theme.css</name><style>/*
* 	Owl Carousel Owl Demo Theme 
*	v1.3.3
*/

.owl-theme .owl-controls{
	margin-top: 10px;
	text-align: center;
}

/* Styling Next and Prev buttons */

.owl-theme .owl-controls .owl-buttons div{
	color: #FFF;
	display: inline-block;
	zoom: 1;
	*display: inline;/*IE7 life-saver */
	margin: 5px;
	padding: 3px 10px;
	font-size: 12px;
	-webkit-border-radius: 30px;
	-moz-border-radius: 30px;
	border-radius: 30px;
	background: #869791;
	filter: Alpha(Opacity=50);/*IE7 fix*/
	opacity: 0.5;
}
/* Clickable class fix problem with hover on touch devices */
/* Use it for non-touch hover action */
.owl-theme .owl-controls.clickable .owl-buttons div:hover{
	filter: Alpha(Opacity=100);/*IE7 fix*/
	opacity: 1;
	text-decoration: none;
}

/* Styling Pagination*/

.owl-theme .owl-controls .owl-page{
	display: inline-block;
	zoom: 1;
	*display: inline;/*IE7 life-saver */
}
.owl-theme .owl-controls .owl-page span{
	display: block;
	width: 12px;
	height: 12px;
	margin: 5px 7px;
	filter: Alpha(Opacity=50);/*IE7 fix*/
	opacity: 0.5;
	-webkit-border-radius: 20px;
	-moz-border-radius: 20px;
	border-radius: 20px;
	background: #869791;
}

.owl-theme .owl-controls .owl-page.active span,
.owl-theme .owl-controls.clickable .owl-page:hover span{
	filter: Alpha(Opacity=100);/*IE7 fix*/
	opacity: 1;
}

/* If PaginationNumbers is true */

.owl-theme .owl-controls .owl-page span.owl-numbers{
	height: auto;
	width: auto;
	color: #FFF;
	padding: 2px 10px;
	font-size: 12px;
	-webkit-border-radius: 30px;
	-moz-border-radius: 30px;
	border-radius: 30px;
}

/* preloading images */
.owl-item.loading{
	min-height: 150px;
	background: url(AjaxLoader.gif) no-repeat center center
}</style><sys_created_by>eric.szonyi_SHARE</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2014-06-17 13:48:31</sys_created_on><sys_id>a49d83ae7919e940f110a6fa63ddf10d</sys_id><sys_mod_count>0</sys_mod_count><sys_updated_by>eric.szonyi_SHARE</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2014-06-17 13:48:31</sys_updated_on><type>local</type><url/></content_css></record_update>

<j:jelly trim="false" xmlns:j="jelly:core" xmlns:g="glide" xmlns:j2="null" xmlns:g2="null">
  <g:evaluate>
     var gr = new GlideRecord('content_block_iframe');
     gr.initialize();
     gr.frame_name = 'gsft_main';
     gr.url = "incident.do?sys_id=${current.sys_id}${AMP}sysparm_view=ess${AMP}sysparm_stack=to_do.do%3Fsysparm_query=active=true%26sysparm_view=ess";
     gr.sizing = 'expand';
     gr.putCurrent();
  </g:evaluate>
  <g:render_content_block_iframe />
  <g:evaluate>
     gr.popCurrent();
  </g:evaluate>
</j:jelly></detail><detail_page display_value="UA2 - Record Detail">405267bf4d98ad80bc95842eaf53541b</detail_page><gauge_page/><media_type/><summary><?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<j:jelly trim="false" xmlns:j="jelly:core" xmlns:g="glide" xmlns:j2="null" xmlns:g2="null">
   <g:evaluate var="jvar_time_text">
     var d1 = current.sys_updated_on.getGlideObject().getRaw();
     var d2 = Packages.com.glide.glideobject.GlideDateTime().getRaw();
     
     var diff = gs.dateDiff(current.sys_updated_on.getDisplayValue(), gs.nowDateTime(), true);
     var msg;
     if (3600 * 12 > diff) {
       var s = Packages.com.glide.ui.jelly.tags.mergedata.HistoryTag2().translatedTimeDifferenceString(d2, d1);
       if (s == null)
         msg = "${gs.getMessage('Just now')}";
       else
         msg = s.toLowerCase() + '${gs.getMessage(" ago")}';
     } else {
       var session = gs.getSession();
       var tf = session.getTimeFormat();
       session.setTimeFormat(" ");
       msg = trim(current.sys_updated_on.getDisplayValue());
       session.setTimeFormat(tf);
     }
     msg;
   </g:evaluate>
   <td>
   <g:content_link type="${jvar_type}" content_link_class="${jvar_content_link_class}">
     ${current.getDisplayValue()} 
   </g:content_link>
   </td>
   <td>${current.short_description.getDisplayValue()}</td>
   <td>${current.state.getDisplayValue()}</td>
   <td>${current.sys_updated_on.getDisplayValue()}</td>
   <td>${current.sys_updated_by.getDisplayValue()}</td>


</j:jelly></summary><sys_created_by>eric.szonyi_SHARE</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2014-05-21 18:22:59</sys_created_on><sys_id>0089894e4d3cadc0bc95842eaf53542e</sys_id><sys_mod_count>2</sys_mod_count><sys_updated_by>eric.szonyi_SHARE</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2014-06-05 19:23:40</sys_updated_on><two_phase>false</two_phase><type>task</type></content_type></record_update>

menu.addQuery('type', 'blocks');
menu.setValue('type', 'horizontal_blocks');
menu.execute();

//update the block records
var ch = new GlideRecord('sys_choice');
ch.addEncodedQuery("nameINjavascript:getTableExtensions('content_block_menu')^element=type^value=blocks");
ch.query();
while (ch.next()) {
    ch.value = 'horizontal_blocks';
    ch.update();
}

<j:jelly trim="false" xmlns:j="jelly:core" xmlns:g="glide" xmlns:j2="null" xmlns:g2="null">


  <g:evaluate var="jvar_count" object="true">
	var cnt = 0;
	var c = new GlideRecord('sc_cart_item');
	c.addQuery('active','true');
	c.addQuery('cart.requested_for',gs.getUserID());
	c.query()
	while (c.next()) {
		cnt += parseInt(c.quantity);
	}
	    var arr = cnt.toString().split('.');
	    cnt = arr[0];
	cnt;

</div>

    var isBootstrapEvent = false;
    if (window.jQuery) {
        var all = jQuery('*');
        jQuery.each(['hide.bs.dropdown', 
            //'hide.bs.collapse', 
            'hide.bs.modal', 
            'hide.bs.tooltip',
            'hide.bs.popover'], function(index, eventName) {
            all.on(eventName, function( event ) {
                isBootstrapEvent = true;
            });
        });
    }
    var originalHide = Element.hide;
    Element.addMethods({
        hide: function(element) {
            if(isBootstrapEvent) {
                isBootstrapEvent = false;
                return element;
            }
            return originalHide(element);
        }
    });
})();</script><sys_created_by>eric.szonyi_SHARE</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2014-06-12 16:36:55</sys_created_on><sys_id>8524ca454d19ed04bc95842eaf535421</sys_id><sys_mod_count>0</sys_mod_count><sys_updated_by>eric.szonyi_SHARE</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2014-06-12 16:36:55</sys_updated_on></sys_ui_script></record_update>

        <script>
            (function() {
                CustomEvent.observe('content_frame.resized', contentFrameResized);
                CustomEvent.observe('content_frame.loaded', contentFrameResized);
                var isFirefox = navigator.userAgent.indexOf('Firefox') > -1;

                function contentFrameResized(name, height) {
                    if (!name)
                        return;

                    var f = $(name);
                    if (!f)
                        return;

                    // avoid using an AND here
                    if (!isFirefox || height == 10)
                        _resize(f, height);
                    else {
                        // delay resize for firefox
                        setTimeout(function() {
                            _resize(f, height);
                        }, 0);
                    }
                }

                function _resize(f, height) {
                    f.height = height;
                }
            })();
        </script>

<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update table="content_css"><content_css action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><name>sport.dynamic.css</name><style>/* header and footer */
div.navbar.navbar-inverse.navbar-fixed-bottom {
    background-color: #${cms.sport.color.footer};
}

div.navbar.navbar-inverse.navbar-fixed-top {
    background-color: #${cms.sport.color.header};
}
div.navbar.navbar-inverse.navbar-fixed-bottom {
    /* border-top: solid 5px #${cms.sport.color.accent}; */
}

/* feedback */
.fm_clean {
    background-color: #${cms.sport.color.accent2};
}

/* page title */
.sport_page_title_text {
    color: #${cms.sport.color.main};
}
/*
td.expert_banner_present, td.expert_banner_future, td.expert_banner_past, TR.io_lable > td {
    color: #${cms.sport.maincolor} !important;
}
*/

/* task counter on todos */
div.noti_bubble {
    background-color: #${cms.sport.color.accent2};
}

/* cart */
#mini-cart-count {
    color: #${cms.sport.color.accent2};
}

/* live feed */
h2.live_feed_name {
    color: #${cms.sport.color.main};
}

/* buttons */
HTML[data-doctype=true] BUTTON, HTML[data-doctype=true] INPUT.button {
    border-color: #${cms.sport.color.button};
    color: #${cms.sport.color.button};
}
HTML[data-doctype=true] BUTTON:hover, HTML[data-doctype=true] INPUT.button:hover {
    background-color: #${cms.sport.color.button};
    color: #ffffff;
}
HTML[data-doctype=true] A.content_list_link {
    color: #${cms.sport.color.accent};
}

/* other elements */
HTML[data-doctype="true"] INPUT:focus, HTML[data-doctype="true"] TEXTAREA:focus, HTML[data-doctype="true"] BUTTON:focus, HTML[data-doctype="true"] INPUT.button:focus, HTML[data-doctype="true"] A.menu:focus, HTML[data-doctype="true"] A IMG:focus, HTML[data-doctype="true"] SELECT:focus {
    border: 1px solid #${cms.sport.color.accent};
    box-shadow: 0px 0px 5px #${cms.sport.color.accent};
}

/* feedback CSS */
#feedback a {
    background: #${cms.sport.color.accent2};
}

#feedback a:hover {
    background: #${cms.sport.color.accent};
}



/*
button, input[type="button"], input[type="submit"], .request_catalog_button, .graphic_button, button.catalog, button.catalog_search, .form_action_button, button#sysverb_new, button#update_work_button
{
    border: 1px solid #${cms.sport.buttoncolor};
    color: #${cms.sport.buttoncolor};
}
button:hover, input[type="button"]:hover, input[type="submit"]:hover, .request_catalog_button:hover, .graphic_button:hover, button.catalog:hover, button.catalog_search:hover, .form_action_button:hover,button#update_work_button:hover
{
    background-color: #${cms.sport.buttoncolor};
}
.btn-default:hover {
    border-color: #${cms.sport.buttoncolor};
}
*/

/* icons */
i {
    color: #${cms.sport.color.icon};
}
</style><sys_created_by>eric.szonyi_SHARE</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2014-06-18 21:48:17</sys_created_on><sys_id>bcd48e0b4d9da144bc95842eaf5354da</sys_id><sys_mod_count>39</sys_mod_count><sys_updated_by>admin_SHARE</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2014-10-03 21:32:18</sys_updated_on><type>local</type><url/></content_css><sys_app_file action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><customer_update>true</customer_update><publish_override/><replace_on_upgrade>false</replace_on_upgrade><restore/><sys_app display_value="Landlord">b9bca8d8eb1121006395c63ca206fe3f</sys_app><sys_code>!!5~S/</sys_code><sys_created_by>eric.szonyi_SHARE</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2014-06-18 21:48:17</sys_created_on><sys_id>2c000cd27da5a100afe443a59ebea897</sys_id><sys_mod_count>1</sys_mod_count><sys_name>sport.dynamic.css</sys_name><sys_parent/><sys_path>!!5~S/</sys_path><sys_policy/><sys_source_deleted>false</sys_source_deleted><sys_source_id>bcd48e0b4d9da144bc95842eaf5354da</sys_source_id><sys_source_table>content_css</sys_source_table><sys_type/><sys_update_name>content_css_bcd48e0b4d9da144bc95842eaf5354da</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>admin_SHARE</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2014-10-03 21:32:18</sys_updated_on></sys_app_file></record_update>

<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update table="content_type"><content_type action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><content_site display_value="UA2">a90ef6b6eb00210093d6c63ca206fe6b</content_site><detail><?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<j:jelly trim="false" xmlns:j="jelly:core" xmlns:g="glide" xmlns:j2="null" xmlns:g2="null">
  <g:evaluate>
     var gr = new GlideRecord('content_block_iframe');
     gr.initialize();
     gr.frame_name = 'gsft_main';
     gr.url = "incident.do?sys_id=${current.sys_id}${AMP}sysparm_view=ess${AMP}sysparm_stack=to_do.do%3Fsysparm_query=active=true%26sysparm_view=ess";
     gr.sizing = 'expand';
     gr.putCurrent();
  </g:evaluate>
  <g:render_content_block_iframe />
  <g:evaluate>
     gr.popCurrent();
  </g:evaluate>
</j:jelly></detail><detail_page display_value="UA2 - Record Detail">405267bf4d98ad80bc95842eaf53541b</detail_page><gauge_page/><media_type/><summary><?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<j:jelly trim="false" xmlns:j="jelly:core" xmlns:g="glide" xmlns:j2="null" xmlns:g2="null">
   <g:evaluate var="jvar_time_text">
     var d1 = current.sys_updated_on.getGlideObject().getRaw();
     var d2 = Packages.com.glide.glideobject.GlideDateTime().getRaw();
     
     var diff = gs.dateDiff(current.sys_updated_on.getDisplayValue(), gs.nowDateTime(), true);
     var msg;
     if (3600 * 12 > diff) {
       var s = Packages.com.glide.ui.jelly.tags.mergedata.HistoryTag2().translatedTimeDifferenceString(d2, d1);
       if (s == null)
         msg = "${gs.getMessage('Just now')}";
       else
         msg = s.toLowerCase() + '${gs.getMessage(" ago")}';
     } else {
       var session = gs.getSession();
       var tf = session.getTimeFormat();
       session.setTimeFormat(" ");
       msg = trim(current.sys_updated_on.getDisplayValue());
       session.setTimeFormat(tf);
     }
     msg;
   </g:evaluate>
   <td>
   <g:content_link type="${jvar_type}" content_link_class="${jvar_content_link_class}">
     ${current.getDisplayValue()} 
   </g:content_link>
   </td>
   <td>${current.short_description.getDisplayValue()}</td>
   <td>${current.state.getDisplayValue()}</td>
   <td>${current.sys_updated_on.getDisplayValue()}</td>
   <td>${current.sys_updated_by.getDisplayValue()}</td>


</j:jelly></summary><sys_created_by>eric.szonyi@snc.admin_SHARE</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2014-05-02 20:01:15</sys_created_on><sys_id>68b967f34dd8ad80bc95842eaf53546a</sys_id><sys_mod_count>11</sys_mod_count><sys_updated_by>eric.szonyi_SHARE</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2014-06-05 18:23:28</sys_updated_on><two_phase>false</two_phase><type>incident</type></content_type></record_update>

sys_update_xml.payload:
truegeneralfalsefalseSport Release NotesVersion 3.14

 

Fixes

  • Fixed script errors in sport_cms_header_login UI macro related to sysparm_login_failed
  • Fixed access issue where ESS user could not display icons
  • Removed header menu and feedback control for users not logged in

 

Version 3.13

 

Fixes

  • Fixed script errors in sport_cms_header_login UI macro related to sysparm_document_key
  • Fixed script errors in Sport Dynamic Header related to sysparm_is_login
  • Fixed Font Awesome style sheet for IE fix
  • Fixed broken Continue Shopping button on cart to redirect to main catalog browse page
  • Fixed Back to Catalog button on checkout screen to redirect to main catalog browse page
  • Fixed IFrame resize issue in IE10

Version 3.12

Fixes

  • De-activated default catalog item icon to prevent override of OOB or customer default
  • Fixed CSS that was causing IFrame height issues and cutting off buttons

Version 3.10

Fixes

  • Fixed issue in IE9 where pages with gsft_main IFrames would wildly resize during mouseover
  • Fixed issue with dynamic CSS failing when user is not authenticated. Processor added to public pages
  • Converted FontAwesome font files to attachments from Customer Uploads to address issues with IE8 src in CSS
  • Fixed issue with dynamic CSS inserting itself into the navigation stack

Version 3.9

Enhancements

  • Added jQuery news scroller functionality
  • Added new dynamic block for homepage ilnk blocks and news
  • Enhanced cms_menu macro to allow custom blocks for Navigation Menus
  • Added second Home page to provide alternate landing page format
  • Added new property to display a language picker in the header

Fixes

  • Fixed issue where social icons would not display in the header
  • Fixed menu block macros to check FontAwesome tags instead of image values
  • Fixed task content type so it can display a record from any extended table

Version 3.8

Fixes

  • Created UI page to address stack issue with blank page on delete from cart
  • Converted cart updating functionality to AJAX calls to fix both add and delete issues

Version 3.6

Enhancements

  • Converted Feedback Me plugin to pure CSS3 Feedback control
  • Applied Bootstrap table style to lists in IFrames
  • Applied Bootstrap styles to info and error messages in gsft_main IFrames

Fixes

Version 3.5

Enhancements

  • Added release notes page
  • Added Todos links to dynamic style sheet
  • Applied Bootstrap styles to all select dropdown elements
  • Renamed properties to include type to facilitate custom properties page

Fixes

  • Re-located inaccessible Add Content link when editing page
  • Themed main page and IFrame submit buttons properly

Version 3.4

Enhancements

  • Added Font Awesome capabilities
  • Converted ALL site icons to font awesome icons
  • Added Font Awesome tag field to Navigation menus

}

    width: inherit;

sys_update_xml.payload:
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update table="content_css"><content_css action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><name>sport.css</name><style>/*
Red #FF0000 (C62126)
Gray #BAC5C7
Black #000000
Yellow #FFF500
*/

/* Extra small devices (phones, less than 768px) */
/* No media query since this is the default in Bootstrap */

/* Small devices (tablets, 768px and up) */
@media (min-width: @screen-sm-min) {

}

/* Medium devices (desktops, 992px and up) */
@media (min-width: @screen-md-min) {

}

/* Large devices (large desktops, 1200px and up) */
@media (min-width: @screen-lg-min) {

}


/* general settings */
@font-face {
    font-family: 'Open Sans';
    font-style: normal;
    font-weight: 400;
    src: local('Open Sans'), local('OpenSans'), url(https://themes.googleusercontent.com/static/fonts/opensans/v8/cJZKeOuBrn4kERxqtaUH3bO3LdcAZYWl9Si6vvxL-qU.woff) format('woff');
}

BODY, TABLE, INPUT, SELECT, BUTTON, INPUT.TEXT, TEXTAREA, INPUT.button, label {
    font-size: 10pt;
    font-family:'Open Sans',Arial,sans-serif;
    color: #000;
}
/* iframe resize fix in IE10 */
body {
    height:auto;
}

iframe {
    /*
    padding-left: 5px;
    padding-right: 5px;
    */
}


HTML[data-doctype=true] A.btn-primary {
    color: #ffffff;
}
/*
.form-all, .form-all label, .form-all input, .form-all select, .form-all button, .form-all textarea {
   font-size: 10pt;
   font-family:'Open Sans',Arial,sans-serif,cursive !important;
}
*/

/* page editor - restore add content link  */
a[onclick="javascript:addHomeContent(this);"] {
    position: fixed;
    top: 75px;
    left: 30px;
    color: #FFF;
    font-weight: bold;
}

/* font-awesome */
.fa-black { color:#000; }

/* properties modal */
body > form > table > tbody > tr:nth-child(1) > td > table > tbody > tr
{
    display:none;
}
body > form > table > tbody > tr:nth-child(2) {
    display:none;
}

/* tooltips */
div.tooltip-inner, div.tooltip, .tooltip-top, .tooltip-in {
    background-color: #FFF500;
    color: #000;
}
.tooltip {
    background:#FFF500;
}
.tooltip-arrow {
    display: none;
}

/* properties page */
.prop-code {
    color: #c62126;
    margin-left: 15px;
}

/* login page */
#loginPage {
    border: 1px solid #C0C0C0;
    border-radius: 10px;
    padding: 25px;
    width: 350px;
    margin-left: auto;
    margin-right: auto;
}
#loginPage > table {
    border-spacing: 10px;
    border-collapse: separate;
}

/* layout elements */
div#sport_main div#dropzone30 {
/*    padding-top:20px;
    padding-right: 10px;
    padding-bottom: 20px; */
    padding-left: 10px;
}
#sport_main {
    margin-top:100px;
}
div#dropzone30 {
    margin-bottom: 25px;
    padding-left: 5px;
    padding-right: 5px;
}
div#page_timing_div.timingDiv {
    display: none;
}
.row {
    margin-left: -9px;
    margin-right: -9px;
}


/* carousel */
.carousel {
    margin-bottom: 0px !important;
    width:1160px;
    margin-left: auto;
    margin-right: auto;
}
div.item.active {
    padding-left: 15px;
    padding-right: 15px;
}
.carousel-chevron {
    margin-top: 300px;
}



/* header */
li.dropdown > a.dropdown-toggle {
    background-color: transparent;
    color: #FFF;
    text-decoration: none;
}
.dropdown-menu>li>a:hover, .dropdown-menu>li>a:focus {
    color: #000;
    background-color: #FFF500;
}
ul.dropdown-menu {
    text-transform: none;
}
.nav .open>a, .nav .open>a:hover, .nav .open>a:focus {
    background-color: transparent;
}
#sport-logo-center {
    position:fixed;
    left:50%;
    top:0px;
    margin-left:-48px;
    /* margin-top:-20px; */
    z-index:10000 !important;

<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update table="content_type"><content_type action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><content_site display_value="UA2">a90ef6b6eb00210093d6c63ca206fe6b</content_site><detail><?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<j:jelly trim="false" xmlns:j="jelly:core" xmlns:g="glide" xmlns:j2="null" xmlns:g2="null">
  <g:evaluate>
     var gr = new GlideRecord('content_block_iframe');
     gr.initialize();
     gr.frame_name = 'gsft_main';
     var url = RP.getParameterValue('uri');
     if (gs.getProperty("glide.cms.catalog_uri_relative", false) == "true")
        url = Packages.com.glide.util.SecurityUtils.enforceRelativeURL(url);

     // make all sc_cat_item not have the search in the CMS in the frame, use the block instead
     if (url.indexOf("?") == -1)
        url += "?";
     url += "&amp;sysparm_no_search=true&amp;sysparm_headless=true";
     gr.url = url;
     gr.sizing = 'expand';
     gr.putCurrent();
  </g:evaluate>
  <g:render_content_block_iframe />
  <g:evaluate>
     gr.popCurrent();
  </g:evaluate>
</j:jelly></detail><detail_page display_value="UA2 - Catalog Detail">200530a54d0d2904bc95842eaf53545e</detail_page><gauge_page/><media_type/><summary><?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<j:jelly trim="false" xmlns:j="jelly:core" xmlns:g="glide" xmlns:j2="null" xmlns:g2="null">
	<g:evaluate var="jvar_item" object="true">
		var ci = Packages.com.glideapp.servicecatalog.CatalogItem.get(current.sys_id);
		ci;
	</g:evaluate>
	<j:if test="${jvar_item.isVisibleStandalone() &amp;&amp; jvar_item.canView()}">
		<g:sc_catalog_item_href />
		<j:if test="${jvar_item.getType() != 'external'}">
			<g:set_if var="jvar_href" test="${empty(jvar_hint)}" false="${jvar_href}&amp;sysparm_processing_hint=${jvar_hint}" />
			<g:evaluate var="jvar_href">
				var t = '${jvar_href}${AMP}sysparm_no_search=true';
				Packages.com.glide.util.StringUtil.urlEncode(t);
			</g:evaluate>
			<g:evaluate jelly="true">
				var pl = new Packages.com.glide.cms.CMSPageLink();
				var targetPage = jelly.jvar_type.getDetailPage(current);
				var pageLink = pl.getPageLink(targetPage);
			</g:evaluate>
			<j:set var="jvar_href" value="${pageLink}?uri=${jvar_href}${AMP}sysparm_document_key=${current.getRecordClassName()},${current.sys_id}" />
		</j:if>
		<j:set var="jvar_target" value="${jvar_item.getTarget()}" />
		<g:set_if var="jvar_iconsrc" test="${jvar_item.getIconSRC() == ''}"
			true="images/icons/catalog_item.gifx" false="${jvar_item.getIconSRC()}" />
		<div class="sc_cat_item_list_container">
			<table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">
				<tr>
					<td valign="top" style="padding-top:3px">
						<span onmousemove="popDiv(event, '${jvar_item.getID()}')"
							onmouseout="lockPopup(event)">
							<img src="${jvar_iconsrc}" alt="${jvar_item.getName()}"></img>
						</span>
					</td>
					<td>
						<j:if test="${!RP.isInteractive()}">
							<span> ${jvar_item.getName()} </span>
						</j:if>
						<j:if test="${RP.isInteractive()}">
							<j:choose>
								<j:when	test="${jvar_target == 'internal' &amp;&amp; jvar_item.getType() == 'external'}">
									<a style="display:block;" href="${jvar_href}" target="gsft_main">${jvar_item.getName()}</a>
								</j:when>
								<j:when test="${empty(jvar_target) || jvar_target == 'internal'}">
									<a style="display:block;" href="${jvar_href}" target="_self">${jvar_item.getName()}</a>
								</j:when>
								<j:otherwise>
									<a style="display:block;" href="${jvar_href}" target="${jvar_target}">${jvar_item.getName()}</a>
								</j:otherwise>
							</j:choose>
						</j:if>
					</td>
				</tr>
			</table>
		</div>
	</j:if>
</j:jelly>
</summary><sys_created_by>eric.szonyi_SHARE</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2014-06-02 20:24:51</sys_created_on><sys_id>027893f94d8d6904bc95842eaf5354d1</sys_id><sys_mod_count>0</sys_mod_count><sys_updated_by>eric.szonyi_SHARE</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2014-06-02 20:24:51</sys_updated_on><two_phase>false</two_phase><type>sc_cat_item</type></content_type></record_update>

<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update table="sys_processor"><sys_processor action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><active>true</active><class_name/><description/><name>SportDynamicCSS</name><parameters/><path>sportdynamiccss</path><roles/><script><![CDATA[String.prototype.replaceAll = function (stringToFind, stringToReplace) {
        if ( stringToFind == stringToReplace) return this;
        var temp = this;
        var index = temp.indexOf(stringToFind);
        while (index != -1) {
            temp = temp.replace(stringToFind, stringToReplace);
            index = temp.indexOf(stringToFind);
        }
        return temp;
    };

//create an array of the properties
var props = ['cms.sport.color.accent','cms.sport.color.main','cms.sport.color.header','cms.sport.color.icon','cms.sport.color.footer','cms.sport.color.accent2','cms.sport.color.button'];
// get the css record - IT SHOULD NOT BE INCLUDED IN THE THEME
var c = new GlideRecord('content_css');
// take the css name as the URL argument
if (c.get('name',g_request.getParameter('name'))) {
  //get the stylesheet
    var text = c.style;
    //match on text wrapped in dollar signs for our properties
	//var matches = text.match(/\$\{(.*?)\}/g);

    //loop through the properties
    for (i=0; i<props.length; i++) {
       //get the property value
       var newValue = gs.getProperty(props[i]);
       //replace the property with the value
	   //text = text.replace('${' + props[i] + '}',newValue);
	   //var re = "/\$\{" + props[i] + "\}/g";
	   //text = text.replace(re,newValue);
		text = text.replaceAll('${' + props[i] + '}',newValue);
    }
    //return the modified stylesheet
  g_processor.writeOutput('text/css',text);
}

]]></script><sys_created_by>eric.szonyi_SHARE</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2014-06-18 21:13:21</sys_created_on><sys_id>f2ecb5474d9da144bc95842eaf5354fe</sys_id><sys_mod_count>35</sys_mod_count><sys_updated_by>admin_SHARE</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2014-07-03 04:47:25</sys_updated_on><type>script</type></sys_processor><sys_app_file action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><customer_update>false</customer_update><publish_override/><replace_on_upgrade>false</replace_on_upgrade><restore/><sys_app display_value="Property Management">b9bca8d8eb1121006395c63ca206fe3f</sys_app><sys_code>!!3M^/</sys_code><sys_created_by>eric.szonyi_SHARE</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2014-06-18 21:13:21</sys_created_on><sys_id>71f84700eb2121006395c63ca206fe22</sys_id><sys_mod_count>0</sys_mod_count><sys_name>SportDynamicCSS</sys_name><sys_parent/><sys_path>!!3M^/</sys_path><sys_policy/><sys_source_deleted>false</sys_source_deleted><sys_source_id>f2ecb5474d9da144bc95842eaf5354fe</sys_source_id><sys_source_table>sys_processor</sys_source_table><sys_type>code</sys_type><sys_update_name>sys_processor_f2ecb5474d9da144bc95842eaf5354fe</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>admin_SHARE</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2014-07-03 04:47:25</sys_updated_on></sys_app_file></record_update>

<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update table="sys_ui_macro"><sys_ui_macro action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><active>false</active><category>cms</category><description>"Horizontal blocks" menu for CMS page headers. </description><media_type/><name>ua_menu_section_blocks_joe</name><sys_created_by>joseph.mccarty@snc_SHARE</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2014-05-28 21:44:42</sys_created_on><sys_id>0bca79144d856504bc95842eaf53545d</sys_id><sys_mod_count>2</sys_mod_count><sys_updated_by>eric.szonyi_SHARE</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2014-06-08 04:49:07</sys_updated_on><xml><?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<j:jelly trim="false" xmlns:j="jelly:core" xmlns:g="glide" xmlns:j2="null" xmlns:g2="null">
    <g:evaluate>
      var sectionGR = new GlideRecord('menu_section');
      sectionGR.addQuery('content_block_menu', menuGR.getUniqueValue());
      sectionGR.addQuery('active', 'true');
      sectionGR.orderBy('order');
      sectionGR.query();
   </g:evaluate>


    <g:cms_menu_functions />
    <j:if test="${sectionGR.hasNext()}">
      <div id="MenuCarousel" class="carousel slide" style="">
        <div class="carousel-inner">

            <j:while test="${sectionGR.next()}">
                <j:if test="${canViewMenu(sectionGR)}">


                  <j:set var="jvar_recordCount" value="${sectionGR.getLocation()}" />
                  <g:set_if var="jvar_class" test="${jvar_recordCount == 0}" true="item active" false="item" />

                  <j:if test="${jvar_recordCount % 3 == 0}">
                    <div class="${jvar_class}" style="background-color:${sectionGR.u_menu_section_color.getDisplayValue()};">


                      <div class="col-md-4">

                      <a href="${jvar_link_url}" target="${jvar_link_target}">

                        <span>Modulus: ${jvar_recordCount % 3}</span>
                        <span>${sectionGR.second_level_text.getDisplayValue()}</span>
                        <j:if test="${sectionGR.image.getDisplayValue()!=''}">
                            <img src="${sectionGR.image.getDisplayValue()}" />
                        </j:if>
                        <label>${sectionGR.name.getDisplayValue()}</label>

                      </a>

                      <j:set var="jvar_t" value="${sectionGR.sys_id}" />
                      <g:evaluate jelly="true">
                        var itemGR = new GlideRecord('menu_item');
                         itemGR.addQuery('menu_section', jelly.jvar_t);
                         itemGR.addQuery('active', 'true');
                         itemGR.orderBy('order');
                         itemGR.query();
                      </g:evaluate>

                      
                      <div>
                        <j:if test="${itemGR.hasNext()}">
                              <j:while test="${itemGR.next()}">
                                  <j:if test="${canViewMenu(itemGR)}">
                                      <g:cms_menu_set_url_and_target />
                                      <a class="ua_menu_block_item" href="${jvar_link_url}" target="${jvar_link_target}">${itemGR.name.getDisplayValue()}</a>
                                  </j:if>
                              </j:while>
                        </j:if>
                      </div>
                    </div> <!-- col-md-4 -->


                  </div> <!-- item -->
                </j:if>
                </j:if>
            </j:while>

        </div> <!-- carousel-inner -->

      <a class="carousel-control left" href="#MenuCarousel" data-slide="prev">&lt;</a>
      <a class="carousel-control right" href="#MenuCarousel" data-slide="next">&gt;</a>




      </div> <!-- carousel slide -->
    </j:if>
    <!-- <div style="clear:both;" /> -->
    <!-- untangle floating divs -->
</j:jelly></xml></sys_ui_macro></record_update>
